<p>Neighborhoods in the foothills like Manitou Springs may face unique challenges with wind exposure affecting both solar panel mounting requirements and HVAC system sizing. The military communities near Peterson Air Force Base and Fort Carson often see high interest in energy efficiency improvements, with residents taking advantage of military-specific financing programs for solar and HVAC upgrades. Downtown and central neighborhoods with smaller lot sizes benefit from high-efficiency heat pump systems and compact solar installations that maximize energy production in limited space.</p>

